creator: Naxum Online Marketing
descriptionHtml:
Zinzino Mobile Application is a predictive action engine created for all Zinzino business partners.

The app tracks all your invitations to contacts and their response back telling you your next follow up step and giving you a suggested text to keep a conversation with each person you're inviting to Zinzino.

You can also follow up with your team members, customers, and to share Zinzino related content with them and others. Inside the system, we provide training for you to reach your highest potential as a Zinzino Independent Partner. And all your actions are rewarded with Activity Points.

Zinzino Mobile Application is a new independent tool so to be able to log in for the first time, you need to create a new password by clicking on ‘Create Password’. There you must type in your Zinzino Partner ID and click ‘Submit’. You will then receive an email with a password reset code.

Today's the day, download and get started now!
